question: Tī lán-e chhèng-giâⁿ, G. Cooksley hō͘-sī D. Beadman, sōaⁿ-liâm lán-e chhèng-giâⁿ siōng ū chin hó ê piâⁿ-kun kiâⁿ-chha̍h ūi, siúⁿ-tiāⁿ 'iâⁿ' chiàu 1, lán-e chhèng-giâⁿ siōng ū chin hó ê piâⁿ-kun kiâⁿ-chha̍h ūi siáⁿ-mih?
TQAN-CHIU-KHUT G1 CHIU-SIK KHE-TOAN KUE-CHHIAU BOAN-LOAN-TU?
Tī chit keng suán-ti̍k 2018 nî ê Kàu-chhat Tāi-sài, siáⁿ-mi̍h hāng-bo̍k ê bōe chhut-liōng tit-tio̍h chòe koân ê chūng-sò͘?

Ūi-tāi ê sî-kan lāi, chha-tiāⁿ chhiúⁿ-chhiⁿ ê soá-tn̂g liû-thêng tú-tú-tiāⁿ kiám-chhiúⁿ koh-khah tn̂g, ia̍h-sī koh-khah té ê soá-tn̂g liû-thêng? Sî-kan thàu-chhun, chit khóan soá-tn̂g liû-thêng sī kah-ì koh-khah tn̂g, ia̍h-sī koh-khah té?
answer: Tī chit ê kái-lio̍k sî-kan lāi, chit khóan chhiúⁿ-chhiⁿ ê soá-tn̂g liû-thêng tāi-khài sī lú-lâi-lú tn̂g. Kāng-khó sî-kan tē 1995 nî 9 goe̍h khai-sí, soá-tn̂g ê tn̂g-té tē 1200 m, tē 1995 nî 11 goe̍h sī piàn-tiâu tiâu cheng-ka kàu tē 2500 m. Hō͘-sî hō͘-sî tńg-lâi tē 1400 m tī 1996 nî 2 goe̍h āu, soá-tn̂g ê tn̂g-té koh cheng-ka, tē 1996 nî 3 goe̍h kiat-sû sī 2400 m ê soá-tn̂g. Chit ê hōe chhut khah bêng-hián ê hōe-chhut, chit khóan chhiúⁿ-chhiⁿ ê chiam-tāi lú-lâi-lú tn̂g, chha-tiāⁿ sī beh chha-khòaⁿ in ê kiap-tōaⁿ ê siân-té tī chit ê sî-kî ê kái-li̍k thàu-chhun.

question: Tui 'Rosehill' tiûⁿ, iâⁿ ê sóa-tn̂g ê miâ ūi-hô?
Tī lāu ê Group 1 (G1) ê ōe-sài tiong, ū kúi-ê phah phah-su (win)?
Māi-iáⁿ kám-ná hō͘-chòe 2 kg, tī só͘-ū chhit-chhun tit-tio̍h "tē 2 miâ" ê pí-sài lāi, che sāng-chāi ê tāng-liōng ē chiâⁿ-chòe kúi-tōa?
Race ê 'Group' koân-chiap (chhin-chhiūⁿ, G1, G2) hām kiam-chhia ê chiap-tū hāng-sò͘ ū bōe chin-chiap ê koan-hē? Chham-ka koân-tiōng pí-sài kap kē-tiōng pí-sài ê kiat-kó chìn-hêng liáu-kái.
answer: Ì-sī ū chi̍t-chióng khoán-chhiúⁿ ê koan-liân-sèng chi-kan tī pí-sài ê Group koân-chiap hām lāi-té ê kiam-chhia ê chiap-tū hāng-sò͘. Ke-chiáu tit-tio̍h siōng koân ê sèng-lu̍t tī siōng koân ê Group 1 (G1) pí-sài, iâⁿ 6 chi 4 (66.7%). Tī kē-tiōng pí-sài (G2, G3, LR), ke-chiáu iâⁿ 4 chi 2 (50%). Che sī kóng ke-chiáu sī chi̍t-ê te̍k-pia̍t-ê pí-sài-chiá, tī siōng kôaⁿ-chi̍t ê pí-sài tiong chiap-tū chin hó.

question: Tī chitê lia̍t-toaⁿ ê sî-kan lāi, ū kúi-ūi bô-kāng ê kî-siâⁿ-chhiòⁿ chài kóe.
Hí-mih Group 1 (G1) saí-chhit, hō͘ sêng-chú khōaⁿ kah pí pa̍t-ê G1 saí-chhit ê tāng-liōng khah-ài hō͘--khah-súaⁿ?
Tī Sóaⁿ ê Sì-chūn, Lē Pún Lú-thong Chhiūⁿ Chūi-chiah Á-boah Hiah-kú?
